    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like a loop that never ends. the grief, the tiredness, the feeling that i failed him... it's just constant. i'm so drained i can't even think straight. sometimes i just lay in bed and think about how much easier it would be if i could just sleep and never wake up. it feels like the only way to actually get some rest.",
