      "content": "i know there are people to talk to but it doesn't change the reality. everything i did was for nothing and now i'm just left with this empty, heavy feeling. it's like i've reached the end of my rope and there's nothing left to give. doesn't it just seem logical that when you're this broken, you'd just want to let go?",
